### Tenant 租户 HTTP API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### Auth: Bearer adex_c93462599a6246a89f55a11b024b1a1a

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = adex_c93462599a6246a89f55a11b024b1a1a

### ListTenants - 批量查询租户
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tenants?name=&status=active&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ListTenants - 分页(透传 next_page_token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/tenants?page_token=&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
